msgid "Why support YunoHost in 2026?"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"YunoHost is a non-profit project that advocates a decentralized Internet, "
"with open, interoperable and sober technologies that respect privacy and "
"(re-)empower the greatest number of people and collectives."
msgstr ""

msgid "Phase 1. Preserving the basics"
msgstr ""

msgid "1.1. Sustain its infrastructure and the team's work dynamics"
msgstr ""

msgid "8,000 €"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Donations are used to pay for the infrastructure costs (YunoHost services "
"and task automation) and to allow the team to meet 2 to 3 times a year."
msgstr ""

msgid "1.2. Facilitate the collective and its projects"
msgstr ""

msgid "12,000 €"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Since 2024, a facilitator (known as “stirring officer”) is in charge to take "
"care of the collective both humanly and administratively, as well as in its "
"external relations."
msgstr ""

msgid "1.3. Maintain the codebase and provide support to the community"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"This budget will fund code and infrastructure maintenance, as well as time "
"spent doing support or reviewing and integrating contributions from new "
"volunteers."
msgstr ""

msgid "Phase 2. Boosting development"
msgstr ""

msgid "31,000 €"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Know more on the main features we plan to develop this year and for which we "
"are seeking funding"
msgstr ""

msgid "2.1. Packaging v3"
msgstr ""

msgid "Funded by NLNet*"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"New iteration on the packaging features with more declarativeness, "
"robustness and effectiveness."
msgstr ""

msgid "* This development is funded by NLNet through NGI0."
msgstr ""

msgid "2.2. Support OIDC"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Replace SSOWat Single-Sign On solution with Authelia and support the more "
"standard OpenID Connect authentication protocol, thus broadening the apps' "
"SSO integration potentiali."
msgstr ""

msgid "2.3. Self-registration feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "10,000 €"
msgstr ""

msgid "5,000 €"
msgstr ""

#, python-format
msgid "50% funded by Code Lutin<br/> through Copie Publique"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Make users able to autonomously register on the server through invite links "
"or a public registering form with admin validation."
msgstr ""

msgid "2.4. Improve the backup and restore feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "20,000 €"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Integrate automatic backup features to YunoHost's core, including remote and "
"encrypted deduplication as well as easy selective restore."
msgstr ""

msgid "2.5. Initiate implementation of self-hosting federation"
msgstr ""

msgid "6,000 €"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"With the self-hosting federation concept, we plan to make it easier to "
"connect to a friend instance in order to provide remote services each other."
msgstr ""

